#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn37.32:2.13"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, pañca ṭhānāni sulabhāni katapuññena mātugāmenā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the five things that are easy to get for females who have made merit.” "

